---
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Ankit Garg"
	description="A short introduction to the background and approach behind this QA work."
>
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="QA work across streaming products, with a focus on release quality, automation, and collaboration."
				align="start"
			/>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Based in New York, with recent work centered on OTT video, cross-platform playback,
						and release quality across web, mobile, and Connected TV.
					</p>
					<p>
						At Vimeo, the work has included playback quality, automation, and release readiness
						across several platforms. One stretch that remains especially meaningful was being part
						of a team that went roughly two and a half years without a critical bug or rollback.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">How Work Gets Done</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						QA is best kept practical. Clear communication, realistic coverage, and just enough
						structure help releases move smoothly.
					</p>
					<p>
						Being approachable and easy to work with matters as much as the test plan. Good QA
						depends on trust across engineering, product, support, and operations, especially when
						issues need quick triage.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">What Matters Most</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>Cross-platform QA for streaming products</li>
						<li>Automation that reduces repetitive regression work</li>
						<li>Release readiness, playback quality, and defect prevention</li>
						<li>Calm collaboration when coordination matters most</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.content :global(ul) {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
	}

	.content :global(li + li) {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
			padding-bottom: 6rem;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
